---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Your checklist is on its way | Sky Lavelle"
  description="Your free project management checklist request has been received."
  noindex
>
  <section class="section min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-3">Your checklist is on its way.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-700">
          Check your inbox. For practical PMO templates and delivery resources, visit Lavelle Pty Ltd.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-100 p-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-1">Lavelle Pty Ltd PMO Resources</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-warm-800">Practical PMO resources, template packs and delivery tools for project managers and delivery leads.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="shrink-0">
            <a
              href="https://lavelleptyltd.com.au/pmo-resources"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-warm-800 hover:bg-warm-900 rounded-md transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
            >
              Browse resources
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <a href="/articles/how-to-rescue-a-failing-it-project" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-1">How to rescue a failing IT project</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 flex-1">A structured approach to diagnosing what has gone wrong and building a credible recovery plan.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">Read &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/project-recovery" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-1">Project recovery advisory</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 flex-1">If the program needs senior attention, an advisory review is a practical starting point.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
